Package: apt-thirdparty-handler
Version: 1.3
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, curl, gpg, gpgv, tar, pkexec | policykit-1
Maintainer: phramusca
Description: One-click installer handler for third-party APT repositories
 Registers the apt-thirdparty:// URI scheme and installs allowlisted third-party
 APT repository entries with explicit user confirmation.

